headline: 1 Top Quantum Computing Stock to Buy Right Now
summary: The next big thing in technology could very well be quantum computing.  Traditional computers operate on bits, which can be in just one of two states.  Quantum computers, by taking advantage of the bizarre properties of quantum mechanics, operate on qubits.
